News.headline: Emirates FA Cup First Round Draw
News.page_title: Emirates FA Cup First Round Draw
News.URL_keywords: Emirates FA Cup First Round Draw
News.short_description: Don't forget the Emirates FA Cup first round draw will be live Monday 17th October from 7pm
News.description:
After the Daggers' 3-1 win over Wealdstone FC yesterday, we have now confirmed our place into the Emirates FA Cup first round draw.
  
We will be draw ball 65 in the first round draw taking place on Monday 17th October at approximately 7:10pm, watch live on BT Sport or BBC 2.

To Find out more or to see the other teams that will be in the draw click here
